<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 18:14:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>俄罗斯将2024-27年油价预测下调至每桶65美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/russia-cuts-oil-price-forecast-65-per-barrel-2024-27-2024-04-23/</link><description>根据路透社周二看到的最新展望，俄罗斯经济部已将该国未来三年的原油出口价格预测下调至每桶 65 美元。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 17:50:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/russia-cuts-oil-price-forecast-65-per-barrel-2024-27-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>开云集团首席财务官表示可能会寻求“增量并购”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/kering-could-pursue-incremental-ma-says-cfo-2024-04-23/</link><description>法国奢侈品集团开云集团首席财务官 Armelle Poulou 周二对分析师表示，其资产负债表健康，可以进行“增量”并购。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 17:43:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/kering-could-pursue-incremental-ma-says-cfo-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>ASMI上调第二季度营收预期，中国订单强于预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asmi-raises-q2-revenue-forecast-chinese-bookings-stronger-than-expected-2024-04-23/</link><description>晶圆加工设备供应商 ASM International (ASMI) 周二上调了今年第二季度的收入预期，理由是中国需求强于预期以及先进逻辑和存储器的销售额增加。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 16:50:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asmi-raises-q2-revenue-forecast-chinese-bookings-stronger-than-expected-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>TikTok已向欧盟提交TikTok Lite风险评估报告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-has-submitted-risk-assessment-report-tiktok-lite-eu-2024-04-23/</link><description>该公司周二表示，已向欧盟委员会提交了关于其新应用 TikTok Lite 的风险评估报告，避免了可能的罚款。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 16:30:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-has-submitted-risk-assessment-report-tiktok-lite-eu-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>开云集团警告上半年营业利润将因 Gucci 销量下滑而下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/gucci-owner-kering-posts-10-drop-q1-sales-sluggish-chinese-demand-2024-04-23/</link><description>法国奢侈品集团开云集团周二表示，由于富有的消费者限制了其明星品牌古驰 (Gucci) 的产品支出，导致第一季度销售额下降，该集团预计上半年营业利润将下降 40% 至 45%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 15:50:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/gucci-owner-kering-posts-10-drop-q1-sales-sluggish-chinese-demand-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>涉嫌中国在欧洲从事间谍活动的案件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/cases-suspected-chinese-espionage-europe-2024-04-23/</link><description>一名欧洲议会助手因涉嫌为中国从事“特别严重”间谍活动而在德国被捕，这是一系列涉及中国在欧洲从事间谍活动的指控事件中的最新一起。北京否认了所有此类指控。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 15:16:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/cases-suspected-chinese-espionage-europe-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>美国反兴奋剂机构呼吁世界反兴奋剂机构在中国游泳丑闻中进行彻底改革</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/usada-calls-wada-overhaul-amid-chinese-swimming-scandal-2024-04-23/</link><description>美国反兴奋剂机构周二表示，在处理中国兴奋剂案件后，世界反兴奋剂机构必须进行彻底改革，以在 2024 年巴黎奥运会之前恢复人们对该全球机构的信心。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 15:07:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/usada-calls-wada-overhaul-amid-chinese-swimming-scandal-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司表示，连接俄罗斯东西部天然气管网的更多工作正在进行中</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/gazprom-says-more-work-underway-link-russias-eastern-western-gas-grids-2024-04-23/</link><description>克里姆林宫控制的能源巨头俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司(Gazprom)周二表示，继上个月在俄罗斯远东地区启动了一条800公里长的管道建设后，其东部和西部管道网络之间的进一步连接工作正在进行中。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 14:49:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/gazprom-says-more-work-underway-link-russias-eastern-western-gas-grids-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国安全设备公司因外国补贴问题在欧盟遭突击搜查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/security-equipment-company-raided-eu-over-foreign-subsidies-concerns-2024-04-23/</link><description>周二，一家中国安全设备公司在其荷兰和波兰办事处遭到欧盟委员会突击搜查，欧盟监管机构加大了对可能接受扭曲性外国补贴的公司的打击力度。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 14:35:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/security-equipment-company-raided-eu-over-foreign-subsidies-concerns-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟议会批准禁止使用强迫劳动制造的产品</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-parliament-approves-ban-products-made-with-forced-labour-2024-04-23/</link><description>欧洲议会周二批准了禁止在欧盟销售、进出口使用强迫劳动制造的商品的规定。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 13:30:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-parliament-approves-ban-products-made-with-forced-labour-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>山特维克收购中国苏州阿诺的多数股权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/sandvik-buys-majority-stake-china-based-suzhou-ahno-2024-04-23/</link><description>瑞典山特维克周二表示，已同意收购中国苏州阿诺精密切削工具技术有限公司的多数股权。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 13:13:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/sandvik-buys-majority-stake-china-based-suzhou-ahno-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>德国央行行长内格尔：资本市场联盟必须成为新欧盟委员会的优先事项之一</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/germanys-scholz-calls-banking-union-europe-2024-04-23/</link><description>德国央行行长和财政部长周二再次呼吁德国在欧盟资本市场联盟方面取得更大进展，以此作为欧洲一体化的下一步要求。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 12:53:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/germanys-scholz-calls-banking-union-europe-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>短缺是铜价上涨至新高的关键</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/shortages-key-coppers-upward-price-trajectory-new-peaks-2024-04-23/</link><description>未来几个月出现的短缺预计将维持铜价上涨至每吨 10,000 美元心理关口的上涨势头。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 11:53:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/shortages-key-coppers-upward-price-trajectory-new-peaks-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>受 Thom Browne 品牌拖累，Zegna 第一季度收入下降 5%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/revenues-zegna-drop-5-q1-dragged-by-thom-browne-brand-2024-04-23/</link><description>意大利奢侈品集团 Ermenegildo Zegna 周二公布，第一季度有机收入下降 5.3%（不包括 Tom Ford Fashion），主要是由于 Thom Browne 品牌销售额下降。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 11:15:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/revenues-zegna-drop-5-q1-dragged-by-thom-browne-brand-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>期待已久的对乌克兰援助即将通过美国国会，武器即将到来</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/long-awaited-aid-ukraine-israel-taiwan-poised-pass-us-congress-2024-04-23/</link><description>众议院突然结束了长达数月的僵局，并在罕见的周六会议上批准了援助，本周，向乌克兰、以色列和台湾提供的数十亿美元的对外援助应该会轻松获得美国参议院的批准。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 10:06:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/long-awaited-aid-ukraine-israel-taiwan-poised-pass-us-congress-2024-04-23/</guid></item></channel></rss>